asap.faceengine.viseme

Class VisemeToMorphMapping

  • java.lang.Object
    • hmi.xml.XMLStructureAdapter
      • asap.faceengine.viseme.VisemeToMorphMapping
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    hmi.xml.XMLStructure

    public class VisemeToMorphMapping
extends hmi.xml.XMLStructureAdapter
    given a viseme number, return the appropriate morph target name. The mapping is read from a resource file. Note: meaning of viseme number dependent on chose viseme set, e.g., Disney 13, or IKP
    Author:
    Dennis Reidsma
